   theoretical ones. The band gap computed with mBJ potential is 2.137 eV
   and the bonding in {[}Sr2F2](2+) and {[}Cu2Te2](2-) blocks is ionic and
   covalent, respectively. Meanwhile the spin-orbit coupling does not play
